Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:02.91,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Well,\NNós iremos,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.41,0:00:05.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭welcome to soteriology.\Nbem-vindo à soteriologia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:09.59,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭This course deals with the Holy Spirit\NEste curso trata do Espírito Santo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:12.09,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and the doctrine of the Holy Spirit,\Ne a doutrina do Espírito Santo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:14.78,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭how the Holy Spirit works in the soul.\Ncomo o Espírito Santo opera na alma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:18.61,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Running all the way from His effectual calling,\NCorrendo todo o caminho de Seu chamado eficaz,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:21.24,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and regeneration,\Ne regeneração,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:24.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭all the way to glorification.\Ntodo o caminho para a glorificação.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:27.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭So it's a very important subject\NEntão é um assunto muito importante
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:31.58,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and I'm glad you're with me.\Ne eu estou feliz que você está comigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.43,0:00:35.62,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭We're going to look at it in some detail.\NNós vamos olhar para isso com algum detalhe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:38.93,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭I think you'll enjoy the class.\NAcho que você vai gostar da aula.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:41.17,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭After all,\NAfinal,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:43.09,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭all of our\Ntodos os nossos
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.94,0:00:45.62,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Christianity,\NCristandade,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.62,0:00:48.12,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭all of our personal religion\Ntoda a nossa religião pessoal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:51.24,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭is just a sham without the Holy Spirit.\Né apenas uma farsa sem o Espírito Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:53.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭So we're very,\NEntão estamos muito,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:56.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭very grateful for the ministry of the Holy Spirit,\Nmuito grato pelo ministério do Espírito Santo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:59.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭I want to begin this\NEu quero começar isso
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:04.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭first lecture with the reading of God's word,\Nprimeira palestra com a leitura da palavra de Deus,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.86,0:01:07.40,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭as we will with each each lecture.\Ncomo faremos a cada palestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.68,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Turn with me,\NVire comigo,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.33,0:01:10.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭please,\Npor favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:14.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭to Romans 8 and I'll read 13 through 17.\Na Romanos 8 e lerei de 13 a 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:18.05,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Romans 8: 13 through 17.\NRomanos 8: 13 a 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:19.90,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭For,\NPor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:23.19,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭if you live after the flesh,\Nse você vive segundo a carne,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:25.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭you shall die.\Nvocê vai morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.51,0:01:27.22,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭But if ye\NMas se você
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:29.29,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭through the Spirit do mortify,\Npelo Espírito mortifiqueis,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:31.78,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭the deeds of the body\Nos feitos do corpo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:34.55,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭ye shall live.\Nvós vivereis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:38.17,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭For as many as are led\NPara tantos quantos são conduzidos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:40.30,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭by the Spirit of God,\Npelo Espírito de Deus,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:43.10,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭they are the sons of God.\Neles são os filhos de Deus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:46.40,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭For you have not received the Spirit\NPois você não recebeu o Espírito
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:48.97,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of bondage again to fear,\Nda escravidão novamente ao medo,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:52.56,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭but you have received the Spirit of adoption\Nmas você recebeu o Espírito de adoção
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:55.26,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭whereby we cry Abba,\Npelo qual clamamos Abba,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.66,0:01:56.86,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Father.\NPai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:02:01.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭The Spirit itself beareth witness with our spirit\NO próprio Espírito testifica com o nosso espírito
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:03.65,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭that we are the children of God,\Nque somos filhos de Deus,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:06.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and if children then heirs,\Ne se filhos então herdeiros,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:10.00,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭heirs of God and joint heirs with Christ.\Nherdeiros de Deus e co-herdeiros de Cristo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:12.38,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭If so be\NSe assim for
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:14.47,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭that we suffer with him,\Nque sofremos com ele,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:19.62,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭that we may also be glorified together.\Npara que também sejamos glorificados juntos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:23.35,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Let's seek God's face in prayer.\NBusquemos a face de Deus em oração.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Lord God,\NSenhor Deus,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:29.36,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭we stand on holy ground,\Nestamos em solo sagrado,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:32.07,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭as we approach this\Nà medida que nos aproximamos disso
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:37.47,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭immense subject of the third person of the Holy Trinity\Nimenso assunto da terceira pessoa da Santíssima Trindade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:42.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and his salvific work in our souls.\Ne sua obra salvífica em nossas almas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:45.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭And we do pray that\NE nós rezamos para que
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.49,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭by the end of this course,\Nao final deste curso,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.54,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭we will have a much more profound appreciation\Nteremos uma apreciação muito mais profunda
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:55.60,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭for the saving ministry of the Holy Spirit,\Npara o ministério salvífico do Espírito Santo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭than we perhaps might have at present\Ndo que talvez possamos ter no momento
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:02.10,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Help us to grow,\NAjude-nos a crescer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:05.83,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭not only in the grace and knowledge of Jesus,\Nnão somente na graça e no conhecimento de Jesus,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:09.12,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭whom the Spirit focuses upon,\Nem quem o Espírito se concentra,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:12.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭but also that we would grow\Nmas também que iríamos crescer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:16.35,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭in the grace and knowledge of the Holy Spirit,\Nna graça e conhecimento do Espírito Santo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:20.18,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭becoming more aware of His work,\Ntornando-se mais consciente de Sua obra,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:22.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭His saving work,\NSua obra salvadora,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:26.14,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and appreciating more profoundly\Ne apreciando mais profundamente
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:28.64,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭the vastness of His ministry\Na vastidão do Seu ministério
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:32.61,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭as he works in sinners and rebels,\Ncomo ele trabalha em pecadores e rebeldes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:36.32,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭such as we all are by nature.\Ncomo todos nós somos por natureza.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:40.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭So Lord bless this class.\NEntão, Senhor abençoe esta classe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:42.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Help me in teaching.\NAjude-me a ensinar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:44.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Help the students in listening,\NAjude os alunos a ouvir,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:47.34,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭learning,\NAprendendo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:50.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and grant that each lecture\Ne conceda que cada palestra
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭may serve to thy glory,\Npossa servir para a tua glória,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:57.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭to our spiritual growth,\Npara o nosso crescimento espiritual,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:03:59.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and to the well-being\Ne para o bem-estar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:03.79,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of our entire being as we journey\Nde todo o nosso ser enquanto viajamos
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭to the never-ending eternity.\Npara a eternidade sem fim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:10.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Be with us now we pray.\NEsteja conosco agora, oramos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:11.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭In Jesus name.\NEm nome de Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Amen.\NUm homem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Well,\NNós iremos,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.97,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭thank you for joining us for this class\Nobrigado por se juntar a nós para esta aula
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:21.65,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and I want to\Ne eu quero
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:25.07,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭begin with the first lecture,\Ncomeçar com a primeira palestra,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:27.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭which is titled: The Study\Nintitulado: O Estudo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:30.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of the Holy Spirit.\Ndo Espírito Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:33.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭The Study of the Holy Spirit.\NO Estudo do Espírito Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:40.41,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭God's Holy spirit was with God's people from the beginning.\NO Espírito Santo de Deus estava com o povo de Deus desde o princípio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.81,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Already in Genesis 1,\NJá em Gênesis 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭verse 2\Nversículo 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:50.75,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭leading them ultimately to their rest\Nlevando-os finalmente ao seu descanso
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:57.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭in Jesus Christ (Isaiah 63 14)\Nem Jesus Cristo (Isaías 63 14)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:00.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭To know the Spirit\NPara conhecer o Espírito
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:05.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭therefore is to stand in continuity\Nportanto, é permanecer em continuidade
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:08.75,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭with the Saints of all ages.\Ncom os santos de todos os tempos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.35,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭God has promised,\NDeus prometeu,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:13.61,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭his Spirit already to Israel,\Nseu Espírito já a Israel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:16.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭His chosen people.\NSeu povo escolhido.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:20.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭We know that in the Old Testament,\NSabemos que no Antigo Testamento,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:24.30,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭various individuals experience a comfort of that Spirit.\Nvárias pessoas experimentam o conforto desse Espírito.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.98,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Think of David,\NPense em Davi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:28.86,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭for example (Psalm 51)\Npor exemplo (Salmo 51)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:31.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭But God promised\NMas Deus prometeu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:36.71,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭a far richer and broader work of the Spirit\Numa obra muito mais rica e ampla do Espírito
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:40.21,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭than we might possibly imagine.\Ndo que poderíamos imaginar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:43.73,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Isaiah foretold of a righteous king\NIsaías predisse um rei justo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:47.23,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭whose administration would be like,\Ncuja administração seria como,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:50.00,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭rivers of waters in a dry place\Nrios de águas em um lugar seco
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:53.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and the transformation of the barren wilderness\Ne a transformação do deserto estéril
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:59.26,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭into a world filled with the fruit of righteousness (Isaiah 32).\Npara um mundo cheio do fruto da justiça (Isaías 32).
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.11,0:06:01.89,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭When the Spirit,\NQuando o Espírito,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:04.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭When the Spirit\NQuando o Espírito
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:07.26,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭is poured out upon us from on high.\Né derramado sobre nós do alto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:11.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭And then he goes on to say in Isaiah 44,\NE então ele continua dizendo em Isaías 44,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:15.88,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭that the Spirit would be poured out on Israel,\Nque o Espírito fosse derramado sobre Israel,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.38,0:06:16.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭like a river\Ncomo um rio
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.12,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of water on dry ground,\Nde água em solo seco,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.97,0:06:24.02,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭irrigating faithless souls to produce a people\Nirrigando almas infiéis para produzir um povo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:28.17,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭who say I am the Lord's.\Nque dizem que sou do Senhor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.02,0:06:30.94,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭And so the Spirit\NE assim o Espírito
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:35.19,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭is the answer of God's covenantal faithfulness\Né a resposta da fidelidade da aliança de Deus
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:37.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭to the chronic problem\Npara o problema crônico
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of Israel's covenant breaking.\Nda quebra da aliança de Israel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:44.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭You find that also in\NVocê encontra isso também em
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.50,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭the Book of Joel\No livro de joel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:50.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭that the Lord would pour out his Spirit upon all his people\Nque o Senhor derramaria seu Espírito sobre todo o seu povo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:54.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭that whosoever would call on the name\Nque todo aquele que invocar o nome
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:57.09,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of the Lord would be saved\Ndo Senhor seria salvo
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:07:01.20,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭(Joel 2:28 to 32).\N(Joel 2:28 a 32).
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:05.58,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭So to study the work of the Holy Spirit\NEntão, para estudar a obra do Espírito Santo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:08.95,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭is to study heavenly work,\Né estudar o trabalho celestial,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.70,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭saving work.\Nsalvando o trabalho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:15.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭And work that abides forever.\NE trabalho que permanece para sempre.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.60,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Now,\NAgora,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.96,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of course,\Né claro,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:21.83,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭in the New Testament age you know,\Nna era do Novo Testamento você sabe,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:25.13,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭that when Jesus rose from the dead\Nque quando Jesus ressuscitou dos mortos
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.77,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and ascended into heaven,\Ne subiu ao céu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:30.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭He poured out His Spirit\NEle derramou Seu Espírito
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:34.57,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭in much larger measures than\Nem medidas muito maiores do que
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.39,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭had previously been known\Njá era conhecido
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.44,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭(Acts 2 17,\N(Atos 2 17,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:44.64,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭through 21 and 33 and 34)\Naté 21 e 33 e 34)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:48.85,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭And Peter after his sermon is interrupted by\NE Pedro depois que seu sermão é interrompido por
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:53.78,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭thousands of people who are under great conviction of sin.\Nmilhares de pessoas que estão sob grande convicção de pecado.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:55.50,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Under it\NSob ele
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:58.55,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and they cried out men and Brethren.\Ne clamaram homens e irmãos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.65,0:08:00.64,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭What shall we do?\NO que devemos fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:03.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Peter said to them,\NPedro disse-lhes:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:06.60,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭repent and be baptized everyone of you\Narrependei-vos e cada um de vós seja batizado
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:09.09,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭in the name of Jesus Christ.\Nem nome de Jesus Cristo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:12.50,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭And you shall receive the gift of the Holy Ghost.\NE você receberá o dom do Espírito Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:15.64,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭For the promise is unto you\NPois a promessa é para você
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:18.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and to your children\Ne para seus filhos
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:21.18,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and to all that are afar off.\Ne a todos os que estão longe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:23.54,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Even as many as the Lord,\NMesmo tantos quanto o Senhor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:28.40,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Our God shall call (Acts 2: 38 and 39).\NNosso Deus chamará (At 2:38 e 39).
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.05,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭And so the rest\NE assim o resto
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.63,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of the New Testament writings,\Ndos escritos do Novo Testamento,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.93,0:08:37.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭particularly Paul's Epistles,\Nparticularmente as epístolas de Paulo,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:41.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭are just filled with the Holy Spirit.\Nsão apenas cheios do Espírito Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:44.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭He speaks often\NEle fala muitas vezes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.25,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭about being born\Nsobre nascer
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:48.99,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of the Spirit such as Galatians,\Ndo Espírito, como Gálatas,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.29,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭4: 29.\N4: 29.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.16,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭And he's talking constantly\NE ele está falando constantemente
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.70,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭about different aspects\Nsobre diversos aspectos
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:59.29,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of the Spirit's saving work.\Nda obra salvadora do Espírito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.89,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Like we just read a few\NComo acabamos de ler alguns
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.49,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of them to you from from Romans 8.\Ndeles para você de Romanos 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:09.51,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭So if we treasure Christ as our only mediator,\NEntão, se valorizarmos Cristo como nosso único mediador,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:13.45,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭we will also treasure the Holy Spirit\Nnós também entesouraremos o Espírito Santo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:16.36,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭as Christ's great gift,\Ncomo o grande dom de Cristo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:18.34,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭which is inseparable from Him,\Nque é inseparável dele,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:21.90,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭to sinners (John 4\Naos pecadores (João 4
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:25.01,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and again John 7).\Ne novamente João 7).
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:28.69,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Jonathan Edwards put it this way.\NJonathan Edwards colocou desta forma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:31.70,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭"The sum of the blessings Christ sought\N"A soma das bênçãos que Cristo buscou
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭by what he did and suffered\Npelo que ele fez e sofreu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:37.22,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭in the work of redemption,\Nna obra da redenção,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:39.90,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭was the Holy Spirit,\Nfoi o Espírito Santo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:43.38,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭the Holy Spirit in His indwelling,\No Espírito Santo em Sua habitação,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:46.66,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭His influences and fruits\NSuas influências e frutos
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:49.19,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭is the sum of all grace,\Né a soma de toda graça,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:50.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭holiness,\Nsantidade,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭comfort and joy,\Nconforto e alegria,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.10,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭or in one word\Nou em uma palavra
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:58.25,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of all the spiritual good Christ purchased\Nde todo o bem espiritual que Cristo comprou
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:01.04,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭for men in this world.\Npara os homens deste mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:04.84,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭And is also the sum of all perfection,\NE é também a soma de toda perfeição,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.71,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭glory,\Nglória,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:07.24,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and eternal joy,\Ne alegria eterna,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.13,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭that he purchased\Nque ele comprou
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:12.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭for them in another world."\Npara eles em outro mundo."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:15.91,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭That's an amazing quote by Edwards.\NEssa é uma citação incrível de Edwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:19.06,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭And it certainly shows us\NE certamente nos mostra
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:22.38,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭that many today are minimizing\Nque muitos hoje estão minimizando
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.28,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭the role of the ministry\No papel do ministério
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:28.15,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of the Holy Spirit as\Ndo Espírito Santo como
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.99,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭integral with the entire\Nintegral com toda
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:33.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭sum of blessings\Nsoma de bênçãos
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:36.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭that God's people receive in salvation.\Nque o povo de Deus recebe na salvação.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:40.08,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭John Brown of Headington\NJohn Brown de Headington
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭put it this way,\Npõe desta forma,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:46.05,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭"Did Christ purchase the Holy Spirit?\N"Cristo comprou o Espírito Santo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:49.58,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Christ purchased the Spirit's gifts,\NCristo comprou os dons do Espírito,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:52.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and influences in applying redemption,\Ne influências na aplicação da redenção,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.11,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭but not his being,\Nmas não o seu ser,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:57.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭which is independent."\Nque é independente."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.38,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭So the work of the Spirit\NAssim, a obra do Espírito
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:04.10,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭in many ways\Nde muitas maneiras
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭is the fruit\Né a fruta
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:08.58,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of Christ's death and resurrection.\Nda morte e ressurreição de Cristo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:10.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭Now,\NAgora,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:13.63,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭salvation in Christ\Nsalvação em Cristo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.81,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭is appreciated and enjoyed therefore\Né apreciado e apreciado, portanto
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:20.33,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭only by knowing the Holy Spirit\Nsomente conhecendo o Espírito Santo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:22.54,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and his saving work.\Ne sua obra salvadora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.34,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭And this is one of the\NE este é um dos
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.55,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭greatest doctrines of the Reformation,\Nmaiores doutrinas da Reforma,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:32.80,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭developed so thoroughly and then even\Ndesenvolvido tão completamente e, em seguida, até mesmo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.87,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭augmented by the Puritans.\Naumentada pelos puritanos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:40.82,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭What a treasure Reformed theology brings us\NQue tesouro a teologia reformada nos traz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.83,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭about the saving ministry of the Holy Spirit.\Nsobre o ministério salvador do Espírito Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.32,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭In fact,\NNa verdade,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:51.01,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭BB Warfield called John Calvin\NBB Warfield chamado João Calvino
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.86,0:11:53.43,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭The Theologian of the Holy Spirit.\NO Teólogo do Espírito Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.92,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭And Warfield went on to claim\NE Warfield passou a reivindicar
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.90,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭the developed doctrine\Na doutrina desenvolvida
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:02.18,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of the work of the Holy Spirit\Nda obra do Espírito Santo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.56,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭is an exclusively Reformation doctrine,\Né uma doutrina exclusivamente da Reforma,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:08.89,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and more particularly a Reformed doctrine,\Ne mais particularmente uma doutrina reformada,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:12.99,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and still more particularly a Puritan doctrine.\Ne ainda mais particularmente uma doutrina puritana.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.31,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭And so,\NE entao,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.13,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭study of the Spirit\Nestudo do Espírito
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:22.40,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭through Reformed experiential soteriology,\Natravés da soteriologia experiencial reformada,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:24.72,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭- that is,\N- isso é,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.67,0:12:27.21,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭salvation that we experience\Nsalvação que experimentamos
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.62,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭by the work\Npelo trabalho
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.74,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭of the Spirit in the soul -\Ndo Espírito na alma -
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.59,0:12:34.47,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭opens up a vast wealth of wisdom\Nabre uma vasta riqueza de sabedoria
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.32,0:12:37.52,Latin,,0,0,0,,‭and joy to the believer.\Ne alegria para o crente.
